1. *Tv* je bila ugašena. (The television was turned off.) 
2. *Tv*om se upravlja daljinskim upravljačem. (The television is controlled by a remote.)
3. Moj otac voli da gleda *tv* uveče. (My father likes to watch television in the evening.)
4. Moj brat je ljubitelj *TV* emisija. (My brother is a fan of TV shows.)
5. Na *TV*-u je bila vrlo interesantna emisija. (There was a very interesting show on the television.)